                            <comment id="17454834" author="paulk" created="Tue, 7 Dec 2021 20:34:35 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Another example:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;assert&lt;/span&gt; ($/$$/$ + &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;x&apos;&lt;/span&gt; + /$$/) == &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;$x$$&apos;&lt;/span&gt;   &lt;span class=&quot;code-comment&quot;&gt;// Unexpected input: &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;$/) == &apos;&lt;/span&gt;$&apos; at line: 1, column: 26&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;And the CST:&lt;br/&gt;
 &lt;span class=&quot;image-wrap&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/attachment/13037091/13037091_screenshot-1.png&quot; style=&quot;border: 0px solid black&quot; /&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17464549" author="paulk" created="Thu, 23 Dec 2021 13:05:36 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;But this works:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;assert&lt;/span&gt; ($/$$ /$ + &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;x&apos;&lt;/span&gt; + /$$/) == &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;$ x$$&apos;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;So, only immediately after a &lt;tt&gt;$$&lt;/tt&gt; is not working?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
